  <compounddef id="BACKGROUND" kind="page">
    <compoundname>BACKGROUND</compoundname>
    <title>BACKGROUND Keyword</title>
    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">BACKGROUND<sp/>integer-expression</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>Sets the current <bold>text background colour</bold> to <computeroutput>integer-expression</computeroutput>. <linebreak/>
 Colours use the standard <bold>VGA 0–15 palette</bold>, emitted via ANSI escape codes. The setting affects subsequent text output (e.g., <computeroutput>PRINT</computeroutput>) until changed or the screen is cleared.</para>
<para><image type="html" name="colours.png"></image>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>Use <ref refid="COLOUR" kindref="compound">COLOUR</ref> to set <bold>foreground</bold> and background together. </para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para><ref refid="GCOL" kindref="compound">GCOL</ref> affects <bold>graphics drawing</bold>, not text.</para>
</simplesect>
<hruler/>
</para>
