<para><heading level="5">Example</heading>
</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".basic"><codeline><highlight class="normal">FOR<sp/>C<sp/>=<sp/>0<sp/>TO<sp/>15</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>BACKGROUND<sp/>C</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>PRINT<sp/>&quot;BACKGROUND<sp/>COLOUR<sp/>&quot;;<sp/>C</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">NEXT</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><heading level="5">Notes</heading>
</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Valid range is <bold>0–15</bold>. Values outside this range are <bold>implementation-defined</bold>.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Background colour persists until changed, even after <ref refid="CLS" kindref="compound">CLS</ref>.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>This statement only affects <bold>text-mode</bold> rendering; use graphics statements for pixel fills.</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><bold>See also:</bold> <ref refid="COLOUR" kindref="compound">COLOUR</ref>, <ref refid="GCOL" kindref="compound">GCOL</ref>, <ref refid="CLS" kindref="compound">CLS</ref> </para>
